      <section eId="sec_11_8_113">
        <num>11-8-113</num>
        <content>
          <p>A contract or modification of a contract for the sale or purchase of a security is enforceable whether or not there is a writing signed or record authenticated by a party against whom enforcement is sought, even if the contract or modification is not capable of performance within one year of its making.</p>
